SOL(1)
======
Jason Lingle <jasonlingle@yahoo.com>

NAME
----
sol(iloquy) --- The programmers' editor of your nightmares

SYNOPSIS
--------
sol [*OPTIONS*] [*file* [...]]

DESCRIPTION
-----------
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Soliloquy will be a highly extensible, non-visual editor with modern features,
which will include:

- Automatic indentation
- Automatic word-wrap
- Syntax highlighting
- Fast line editing
- Multiple buffers
- Infinite undo

"Primary Keys" Meta Keymap
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Left hand:
----------------
+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
| Q        | W        | E        | R        | T        |
| Exchg    | Set mark | View page| View page| Permute  |
| mark/cur |          | up       | down     | chars    |
|          |          |          |          | Transpose|
| Pop mark | Push mark| To TOF   | To EOF   | units    |
+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+-+
  | A        | S        | D        | F        | G        |
  | Show open| Shw close| Show prev| Show next| Show sur-|
  | block    | block    | line(s)  | line(s)  | ounding  |
  |          |          |          |          | Ask how  |
  | x 5      | x 5      | x 5      | x 5      | many     |
  +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+-+
    | Z        | X        | C        | V        | B        |
    | Activity | Parent   | Replace  | Search   | Yank and |
    | to bottom| activity |          | forward  | advance  |
    |          |          |          |          |          |
    | From bot | Child    | In region| Backward | No adv   |
    +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
----------------

Right hand:
----------------
+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
| Y        | U        | I        | O        | P        |
| Undo     | Forward  | Backward | Kill bkwd| Kill fwd |
|          | group    | group    | group    | group    |
|          | To target| To target| To target| To target|
| Redo     | group    | group    | group    | group    |
+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+-+
  | H        | J        | K        | L        | ;        |
  | Home     | Backward | Forward  | Kill bkwd| Kill fwd |
  |          | unit     | unit     | unit     | unit     |
  | Kill to  | To target| To target| To target| To target|
  | home     | unit     | unit     | unit     | unit     |
  +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+-+
    | N        | M        | ,        | .        | /        |
    | End      | Backward | Forward  | Kill bkwd| Kill fwd |
    |          | s-expr   | s-expr   | s-expr   | s-expr   |
    | Kill to  |          |          |          |          |
    | end      | Exit curr| Exit curr| Kill curr| Kill prnt|
    +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
----------------
